### Recommended CSS Patterns (Common in These Exercises)

1. **Using grid-template-areas (Sabse Clean)**
```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr 300px;
  grid-template-areas:
    "sidebar main aside"
    "sidebar main aside";
  gap: 20px;
}

.sidebar { grid-area: sidebar; }
.main    { grid-area: main; }
.aside   { grid-area: aside; }
```

2. **Responsive with auto-fit (Bohot Useful)**
```css
.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}
```

3. **Individual Item Alignment**
```css
.item {
  justify-self: center;   /* horizontal */
  align-self: end;        /* vertical */
}
